Homunculus α is an extremely large, semi-humanoid homunculus with two arms, and highly textured reddish-purple skin that resembles raw muscle. Its arms end in milti-toed-toed feet, which it uses for both locomotion and attacks; however, it does not possess any hind legs and appears to be attached to the ceiling of the Ark Mall due to the fact that it is not fully-formed. On its back it has a large, bone-like shell covered in tall spikes, and its chest is encased by rib-like structures extending around both sides from the back. It has a small head relative to its body size, with four eyes
(two eyes per socket). The most prominent feature of its head is the large, sharp-toothed jaw, which extends well into the neck and is capable of opening both normally in a horizontal way as well as vertically across the top of the head, allowing it to split its head into four flaps, fully exposing the mouth and throat.

preview_comments.text: Wow. Well I am 45 and still finding my place. A few years back I got a diagnosis that said I had brain damage from the multiple concussions as a child and years of PTSD inducing trauma from my stepfather. I go through jobs like a fat kid through cake(its ok Im technically obese) and yet my wife loves me and my kids tolerate my humor. Yet, I am still searching and working towards a better me. Now, am I where I want to be? Of course not but I am alive and doing much better than I would have if I had just stopped trying years ago. Take breaths when you need to cool down, take a nap when youre tired but make sure you get fresh air and enjoy the simplest of things.
♥️♥️♥️🐈🐈🐈 have all the warm and fuzzies.

🤔Une PlayStation 5 Pro au lancement de la PS5 ?🤔
.
C'est par le biais du journaliste japonais Zenji Nishikawa que nous apprenons la nouvelle ce matin. Ce dernier profite d'un stream youtube pour expliquer que lors du dernier Computer Entertainment Developers Conference (CEDEC) qui a eu lieu au début du mois, il a entendu certaines informations surprenantes.
.
Selon lui, Sony lancerait deux PlayStation 5 de manière simultanée afin de satisfaire tous les joueurs. L'une d'elles serait moins chère, mais moins puissante afin de contenter le public qui ne recherche pas la puissance à tout prix, alors qu'une seconde serait l'équivalent du modèle Pro de la PlayStation 4.
.
Cette dernière serait vendue beaucoup plus cher que la fourchette des 400 dollars annoncés et serait avant tout destinée à un public élitiste. À l'heure actuelle, impossible de savoir si le journaliste dit vrai ou s'il cherche juste à se faire mousser sur le web.
Il faudra donc attendre le prochain E3 ou un événement dédié à la machine pour en savoir plus.

caption.text:
[𝚘𝚌]
Guys, I tried. I really did. I tried my best to give Mario Kart Tour a fair shake. But like, it’s most definitely not good? Like at all?

Controls are really stupid. Basically, you get the choice of either being allowed to only drift or only turn, with no middle ground. Bc of that, the game feels really clunky and awkward, especially on slower speeds.

The game is also 100% pay to win. I can’t see how that could even be debated. Entire game is rigged on a gacha system that boosts your power with better gear, so you’ll always just do better if you’ve pumped more money in the game. Gold pass is also a thing, and it’s required if you want to play 200cc. It’s fucking 60 dollars a year, so I beg you, please don’t buy it. That’s the price of an actual, full, complete game that you can own forever.

Finally, it’s a Mario kart without multiplayer. I don’t care if it’s coming later, a Mario kart game shipping out without multiplayer is absurd. That’s, like, the entire fun part about Mario kart. That would be like a doom game shipping without any weapons.

Overall, Tour has left a really really sour taste in my mouth. Definitely the worst Nintendo mobile game imo, by quite a bit.

caption.text:
[SCORE ATTACK]
⠀
Game: Untitled Goose Game (2019)
Song: Prelude No. 12: Minstrels
Composer: Claude Debussy / @dan.golding
Developer: House House
⠀
Really interesting article from @verge on Untitled Goose Game and how it adapted this Debussy track for its dynamic soundtrack. You can access the full article via the link in our bio, but here's a snippet:
⠀
"To start, Golding began by recording two versions of the “Prelude”: one played normally, and one with a much lower, softer energy. The tracks were then split up into different “stems,” or sections, at the same parts.
⠀
"The stems were then matched up to the game, which operates in three states: the first is a silent state, where the goose is just hanging out, not doing anything; in the second state, the 'low energy version' is performed as the goose is plotting and scheming, moving closer to his prey; and the third state is when you’re being actively chased, which is the performance you’d hear on a record. The game chooses which version to play depending on what’s happening — so taking into account all the different ways the stems can be matched together, that means the amount of different versions you can hear is 'a number with, like, 52 zeroes,' Golding says. ⠀
"'One of the beauties of the game is that nobody’s gonna get the same performance.'"
⠀

◾The Legend of Zelda : Link's Awakening
.
Mon avis en quelques mots 🙂
.
Un jeu toujours aussi plaisant à jouer, avec son gameplay indémodable, ses donjons excellents, une bande-son magnifique avec de supers réorchestrations !
.
Un peu moins fan de la DA (toute "mignonne" 🤢) par contre qui à mes yeux rend le jeu moins sombre et mélancolique qu'auparavant sur Game Boy, c'est regrettable...
.
Un peu BEAUCOUP moins fan aussi du jeu qui rame, faut pas déconner Mr Nintendo hein... ^^
.
Malgré tout et même si je préfère encore l'original, je trouve que ce remake vaut clairement le coup autant pour ceux qui ne l'ont jamais fait que pour ceux qui comme moi l'ont connu à l'époque 🙂
.
Maintenant vu le succès de ce remake, si Nintendo pouvait nous en faire un autre de A Link to the Past ce serait le top du top svp merci 😁
.
🧝‍♂️🧚‍♀️❤🗡🛡🏝🐳🦉
.

#Gamefemerides
Hace  5 años es lanzado Hyrule Warriors (Zelda Warriors en Japón). Es un hack ‘n’ slash desarrollado por Omega Force con colaboración de @teamninjastudio para Wii U de @Nintendo . El juego es una colaboración entre @koeitecmous y Nintendo, y es un crossover entre Dynasty Warriors y The Legend of Zelda. 
Es uno de los mejores vendidos de Wii U. Un port actualizado conocido como Hyrule Warriors: Hyrule All-Stars fue lanzado para Nintendo 3DS en 2016. Un port mejorado, Hyrule Warriors: Definitive Edition, fue lanzado para Nintendo Switch en mayo de 2018.

Contra Rogue Corps
.
Not a great welcome back to the series.. but I like the classic Konami art style of the game box 👍🏻
.
Also I liked the comic style of the story cutscenes .
The game is not that good or bad.. my score is 5.5/10
.
Also I recommend to buy Blazing Chrome because that game really looks like a Contra game
.
So don't buy it if you are not a fan of the series or to add it to the Collection .
.
كونتر روق كوربس
.
ليست افضل لعبة للسلسلة.. لكن اعجبتني طريقة رسم الآرت الكلاسيكيه على الغلاف
.
اعجبني طريقة عرض القصة في اللعبة بأسلوب الكوميكس
.
اللعبة ليست بذلك السوء.. وتقيمي لها ٥.٥/١٠
.
كما وانصح بشراء لعبة بلايزنق كروم وذلك لأنها اقرب لسلسلة ألعاب كونترا الأصلية
.
لا تشتري اللعبة الا اذا طنت من مجبي السلسلة او لضمها لمجموعة ألعاب كونترا
.
.

O TBT de hoje não poderia ser mais legal do que relembrar desse game maravilhoso e divertido de duas gerações atrás. Guitar hero, foi um game de explodir cabeças em época das poucas locadoras de games que ainda restavam, já que se via o game competindo nesse tipo de lugar com outros games gigantes : GTA : San Andreas e Pro evolution Soccer. Quem jogava se sentia um verdadeiro astro do Rock ainda mais quando se jogava com o controle na versão de Guitarra, aí pronto.. Eram horas e horas na frente da TV sem piscar pra não errar nenhuma nota 😵. Se você lembra de músicas como : Slow Ride, Story of My Life, Rock and Roll all night da banda Kiss e histórica batalha com Tom Morello, você está ficando velho!! 😉

Não deixe de seguir a @99fichas para ficar por dentro do mundo dos games🎮

💚 My Stardew Valley Farmer 💚
.
this took a lotttttt more effort than I was expecting. I also got this idea from @krillustration so all credit goes to them for the inspiration!
.
can I just say, I think it’s hilarious that one of my best friends is the Wizard 😂 he’s so rude but I love it! Shane also almost made the cut, but not quite. and f*** the green slimes 😑 actually, ALL coloured slimes can go to hell lol they’re so annoying...
.
ANYWAYS! I really pushed myself with this one and made sure I stepped out of my comfort zone and I’m so glad I stuck it out til the end. two years ago if you told me I would eventually design a character with just a pixel icon to go off of (or just design an entire character at all) I probably wouldn’t have believed you... I know there’s so much more room for improvement but I’m glad that I can personally see my own growth in my pieces 😇
.
PS, if you play Stardew Valley and wanna talk about the game slash your character in it, hit me up 👀 lol
.

Nendoroid de Link du jeu The Legend of Zelda : "Breath of the Wild". Cette édition DX est une version spéciale qui comprend des éléments supplémentaires pour vous aider à recréer encore plus de scènes du jeu. Fabriquée par GoodSmile Company et mesure 10 cm.
2 visages, un arc avec des flêches et son carquois, une épée et son fourreau ainsi qu’un bouclier
La tablette Sheikah  est également incluse. Cette Edition DX est également livrée avec une hache, une massue, une cuisse de poulet, sa capuche et même un cheval sur lequel Link peut monter.
